code: public void test11DebDependencies() {     assumeTrue(Platforms.isDPKG()).     final Shell sh = new Shell().     final Shell.Result defaultResult = sh.run("dpkg -I " + getDistributionFile(DEFAULT_DEB)).     final Shell.Result ossResult = sh.run("dpkg -I " + getDistributionFile(OSS_DEB)).     TestCase.assertTrue(Pattern.compile("(?m)^ Depends:.*bash.*").matcher(defaultResult.stdout).find()).     TestCase.assertTrue(Pattern.compile("(?m)^ Depends:.*bash.*").matcher(ossResult.stdout).find()).     TestCase.assertTrue(Pattern.compile("(?m)^ Conflicts: elasticsearch-oss$").matcher(defaultResult.stdout).find()).     TestCase.assertTrue(Pattern.compile("(?m)^ Conflicts: elasticsearch$").matcher(ossResult.stdout).find()). }
